@host = http://localhost:3000
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api/v1
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### ERP MODULE - Enterprise Resource Planning
### ============================================

### PRODUCTS - List All
GET {{baseUrl}}/erp/products?page=1&limit=20&category=electronics
Authorization: {{token}}

### PRODUCTS - Create Product
POST {{baseUrl}}/erp/products
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Industrial Motor",
  "description": "High-performance industrial motor",
  "category": "electronics",
  "sku": "MOT-IND-001",
  "quantity": 100,
  "reorderLevel": 20,
  "unitCost": 450.00,
  "retailPrice": 750.00,
  "supplier": "supplier-uuid",
  "weight": 15.5,
  "dimensions": "30x20x25cm"
}

### Notes:
### - All endpoints require authentication
### - Replace UUIDs with actual IDs from your database
### - Categories: electronics, mechanical, supplies, tools, other
